          "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The purpose of health care is promoting, maintaining, monitoring, or restoring health.</span></span></span></p>"
