          "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The manager focusses on the Activity.</span></span></span></p>"
